呢d就係能手足既態度？<br />\n唔係想屌人，但係想問你地，對得住咁多個月比人拉既手足嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Vnzon4P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnzon4P.jpg&h=3ef214f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d93a4f38bf21dbdab2cb3f9caf40e64e602a31b2","tid":1504710,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"係溫室長大既香港人<br />\n係咪永遠都唔醒？定扮瞓？<br />\n<br />\n對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}